A step-change improvement in HT electrolysis, enabling additional commercial roll-out of HT electrolysers post 2025.
Improvement of AC electric efficiency above 90%HHV, which is well above MAWP KPI value for HTE in 2023, thanks to the thermal coupling with a heat source to avoid the energy consumption for steam production. Thanks to this, the OPEX will be much improved as compared to the KPI 1 set for PEM and alkaline electrolysis;
